{"tid":1417287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"甘地：「暴力為無法克制自己的野獸所擁有。」「非暴力才是人類的證據，真正有勇氣的證明。」","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T08:25:22.000Z","uid":5549,"like":4,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5f210f7dc74143aafaefc6e55047cf6c8bb734e1","tid":1417287,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"「暴力為無法克制自己的野獸所擁有。」「非暴力才是人類的證據，真正有勇氣的證明。」"},{"pid":"987fe4385c51790ba150fc7dceb06f1064c1b313","tid":1417287,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"「戰爭除了強權的法則之外，不知道任何法律。&hellip;&hellip;自然的力量是以一種神秘的方式發揮作用的。我們只能從類似事件的已知結果來推測未知的後果，從而了解這種神秘的方式。&hellip;&hellip;人類只有通過非暴力才能擺脫暴力。只有仁愛才能克服仇恨。以牙還牙只會擴大和加深仇恨。」"},{"pid":"ab1289c3ba5b0e9ea5134b39e6754bc30b6fec90","tid":1417287,"uid":15605,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"對住支那講非暴力，器官都摘撚埋你"},{"pid":"3b2cea8f0f338878cf2ba8adaff3dc2c90ffada9","tid":1417287,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:19:39.000Z","msg":"「寧肯在自己身上忍受傷害&hellip;&hellip;是非暴力的要素，我們選擇它來取代對他人的暴力。並不是因為我低估生命的價值&hellip;&hellip;而是因為我知道，這樣做從長遠來看犧牲的生命是最少的&hellip;&hellip;使這個世界由於他們的獻身而在道德方面更加充實。」"},{"pid":"fb411ec83b4fee7a0f9cf5a67222ffbfcfeb499c","tid":1417287,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"「當我絕望時，我會想起：在歷史上，只有真理和愛能得勝，歷史上有很多暴君和兇手，在短期內或許是所向無敵的，但是終究總是會失敗。好好想一想，永遠都是這樣。」"},{"pid":"e8161368f9e6fa9a2db814dfea8bab2b76367d9e","tid":1417287,"uid":195570,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"樓主，你真係傻撚左，行街講呢d已經俾人屌到老母都潮吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717df9301760bbb6a2372fe476a7af4ac30e54c7","tid":1417287,"uid":61577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"踏在漫長路上憑友情<br />\n活在銀河內全憑著愛<br />\n終於一天必會得勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cddc776889e18de34f625c327107209c4f8a608","tid":1417287,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"重組警隊 獨立調查<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n堅守香港 保衛家園<br />\n<br />\n[公投] 口號唔止得一個嘅！比多幾個啦！重組警隊 獨立調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416741</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f93dd2f59ad63da6ce8cfe648f4c23e776b760bd","tid":1417287,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"甘地罷交稅，希望樓主發起全民罷交稅運動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ab799ca7cd625f180c9f34ec4901c7d70f7e00","tid":1417287,"uid":51620,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ab1289c3ba5b0e9ea5134b39e6754bc30b6fec90","tid":1417287,"uid":15605,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"對住支那講非暴力，器官都摘撚埋你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:31:47.000Z","msg":"對英國老就有用"},{"pid":"b8c41396c632699dfac9a8dd392c99d93bd8fef8","tid":1417287,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7e737b6006dd5d388e310316d38c5ae5166bcb","tid":1417287,"uid":201031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"如果甘地係支那搞獨立<br />\n十條命都唔夠死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9c2eaedcf9ace578d1699955f35b956663082f","tid":1417287,"uid":34970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"勇武唔等於暴力"},{"pid":"1b785f482070fef77391c9f5362c26aa1eeb29e1","tid":1417287,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4ab799ca7cd625f180c9f34ec4901c7d70f7e00","tid":1417287,"uid":51620,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ab1289c3ba5b0e9ea5134b39e6754bc30b6fec90","tid":1417287,"uid":15605,